There was one other sighting in Killeen on or around September 8th 2012
Summary: Low fly over of reflective crescent followed by low flyover by flying wing
divs: Sighting DetailsA friend of mine while having friends over noticed an object flying well below cloud coverage and very fast, the object seemed to match the same colors as the night sky and clouds as it flew. This Object was described to me as crescent shaped. about 20 seconds later the object vanished. THEN 20 minutes later, a flying wing object passed overhead with pulsating dim lights, it was flying much slower than the first object, but in the same path.
